OL,3,CAngry residents stage protest over
OL,4,Creturn to Barton House
OL,6,FResidents of a tower block in Bristol
OL,7,Fwho were told to leave their homes due
OL,8,Fto safety concerns have staged a
OL,9,Fprotest on City Hall.
OL,11,FAngry with the way they say they've
OL,12,Fbeen treated, and unsure whether their
OL,13,Fhomes will ever be truly safe,
OL,14,Fresidents of Barton House in Barton
OL,15,FHill went inside the Bristol City
OL,16,FCouncil building on Friday 26 January
OL,17,Fto demand answers.
OL,19,FMore than 400 people - including
OL,20,Faround 100 children - their homes on
OL,21,Fthe evening of Tuesday 14 November.
