OL,6,FFollowing an initial survey, it was
OL,7,Ffeared that structural issues could
OL,8,Fput the building at risk of collapse
OL,9,Fin the event of a fire.
OL,11,FMore detailed surveys have since
OL,12,Frevealed the problems were not as
OL,13,Fsevere as thought, and safety work,
OL,14,Fincluding the installation of a
OL,15,Fcentral fire alarm system, additional
OL,16,Ffire proofing in 42 flats and testing
OL,17,Ffor Legionella bacteria is now
OL,18,Funderway to make the building safe for
OL,19,Fresidents' to return
