OL,6,FDespite this, nearly half of the
OL,7,Fhouseholds at the protest on Friday 26
OL,8,FJanuary said they do not want to
OL,9,Freturn.
OL,11,FOne resident told ITV News West
OL,12,FCountry: "We don't feel safe, us as
OL,13,Fparents especially don't feel safe
OL,14,Fwhen we're telling our kids oh you've
OL,15,Fgot to leave it's dangerous and now
OL,16,Fwe're suddenly fine again.
OL,18,F"I don't feel safe to come back"
