OL,6,FAnother resident, Mohamed Ali, has
OL,7,Fbeen staying in temporary
OL,8,Faccommodation at a Holiday Inn in the
OL,9,Fcity since November.
OL,11,FHe had to take his daughter to A and E
OL,12,Fwith an illness recently - a
OL,13,Fconsequence he believes of their ever
OL,14,Fchanging situation.
OL,16,FThe march was organised by the union
OL,17,FAcorn and 40 households have signed a
OL,18,Fpetition saying they don't want to
OL,19,Fmoved back to Barton House.
