OL,6,FAnother resident said: "No- because
OL,7,Fthe building has internal problems, we
OL,8,Fhave problems with the windows, we
OL,9,Fhave problems with doors, its not safe
OL,10,Fto go back in."
OL,12,FThe council has said they will only
OL,13,Fask people to move back when engineers
OL,14,Fand fire service deem the building
OL,15,Fsafe.
