OL,6,FOn Wednesday 10 January, at the
OL,7,Fmeeting where residents were told they
OL,8,Fwould be moving back into Barton
OL,9,FHouse, Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees said:
OL,10,F"The evacuation was necessary because
OL,11,Fof the evidence we had available.
OL,13,F"A representative from Avon Fire and
OL,14,FRescue confirmed that the action we
OL,15,Ftook was appropriate and proportionate.
OL,17,F"We were not taking risks with
OL,18,Fresidents' lives.
